# Monorepo Structure Guide

This project uses a monorepo structure with the following main directories:

- [apps/](mdc:apps): Application entry points, including the main web and server apps.
- [packages/](mdc:packages): Shared packages for API, authentication, database schemas, email, and UI components.
- [tools/](mdc:tools): Configuration and utility tools for development, testing, and build processes.

See [README.md](mdc:README.md) for more details on project setup and usage.
